You know why? ⬇️

Incline Smith press chest grow karne ke liye isliye better hai kyunki yeh upper chest ko specifically target karta hai, jo aksar logon ka weak point hota hai. Smith machine ka fixed path hota hai, jisse aapko balance ka tension nahi hota, aur aap pure focus ke saath chest squeeze kar sakte ho.

Isse mind-muscle connection strong hoti hai, aur constant tension milta hai muscle par. Aap safely heavy weight ya failure tak train kar sakte ho, bina spotter ke. Plus, yeh movement mein shoulder aur triceps ka kam involvement hota hai, jo flat bench press mein zyada hota hai.
